review:
Very hygienic clinic.
Treatment is given after explaining everything in detail. 
I got my dental implants done at dentavenue.
Got dental implants done for my father. The treatment was done flawlessly. We are very happy. Dr Akshay and Dr saundya are very professional

At a dental clinic located in Chembur, Mumbai, my son received Teeth Braces treatment from Dr. Saudnya Rudrawar. The treatment process was incredibly smooth and executed to perfection. Although the treatment required a significant amount of time, the end result was well worth the wait. My son's previously misaligned teeth are now straightened, resulting in an improved and confident smile.
Had a zirconia crown treatment; durable and natural-looking results. Highly recommended .  The clinic's ambiance is pleasant and comforting, making the entire experience stress-free.
Visited for teeth whitening; impressive results and friendly staff.   Best in their field.  Much knowledgeable & experienced
My tooth bridge is perfect; they did an excellent job with the fitting. I definitely recommend them
